  <li>Provide better error reporting when generating sites (<a href="https://github.com/jekyllresources/jekyllresources.github.io/issues/1253">#1253</a>)</li>
  <li>Latest posts first in non-LSI <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">related_posts</code> (<a href="https://github.com/jekyllresources/jekyllresources.github.io/issues/1271">#1271</a>)</li>
